    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/e57866859e132e3a6fc03bcbde433277.poster.avif?t=1765912969\" width=800 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/e57866859e132e3a6fc03bcbde433277.webm?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/e57866859e132e3a6fc03bcbde433277.mp4?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Clyde, a former detective who, after an assassination attempt, takes the path of a samurai. He wears a mask to hide his identity and thanks to this he infiltrates the gang of his nemesis. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete missions to eliminate rivals in the city to increase your prestige in the group. Investigate your last unfinished case. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go through all the trials and finally restore justice. You are the best assassin in DreamCity. You are unshakable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/6d2b2fb43fb3f34bb7fade2c6e79af2f.apng?t=1765912969\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/6d2b2fb43fb3f34bb7fade2c6e79af2f.poster.avif?t=1765912969\" class=\"bb_img\" width=680 height=105 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>USE YOUR WITS:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy your enemies using the environment of the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/89443d84a76b08e1fdfe782d9809ed7e.poster.avif?t=1765912969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/89443d84a76b08e1fdfe782d9809ed7e.webm?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/89443d84a76b08e1fdfe782d9809ed7e.mp4?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE SHADOW IS YOUR BEST ALLY:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide in the shadows from enemy eyes and then attack stealthily!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/61484b48cdedea16f7b696eae462b0a1.poster.avif?t=1765912969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/61484b48cdedea16f7b696eae462b0a1.webm?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/61484b48cdedea16f7b696eae462b0a1.mp4?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND OUT THE STORY:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the story of a man who lost everything and set out on a path of retribution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/dcc013db4e2d6d8ce702c75fc19c2ee4.poster.avif?t=1765912969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/dcc013db4e2d6d8ce702c75fc19c2ee4.webm?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/dcc013db4e2d6d8ce702c75fc19c2ee4.mp4?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EAT A LOT AND DON'T GET FAT:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat pizza with coke. In short, eat whatever you can find to restore your health and stay in battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/06744536004639719977fbccb746dcb5.poster.avif?t=1765912969\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/06744536004639719977fbccb746dcb5.webm?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265100/extras/06744536004639719977fbccb746dcb5.mp4?t=1765912969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
